text: Edward Hastings (1849 - 31 May 1905) was an Australian cricketer. He played two first-class cricket matches for Victoria between 1875 and 1878. ==See also== * List of Victoria first-class cricketers ==References== ==External links== * Category:1849 births Category:1905 deaths Category:Australian cricketers Category:Victoria cricketers Category:Place of birth missing
